  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2759900/extras/3e2987d95a497ac8eb513390b721555f.apng?t=1749946732\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2759900/extras/3e2987d95a497ac8eb513390b721555f.poster.avif?t=1749946732\" class=\"bb_img\" width=600 height=90 /></picture></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2759900/extras/baa022df344ba968f360309a57916221.poster.avif?t=1749946732\" width=600 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2759900/extras/baa022df344ba968f360309a57916221.webm?t=1749946732\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2759900/extras/baa022df344ba968f360309a57916221.mp4?t=1749946732\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Five goofy little adventures spanning a variety of genres (5, in fact) await! Even if these games <i>really</i> sucked that's not a half-bad deal!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2759900/extras/4189c14c0fd2c2a67a454ddee4777424.avif?t=1749946732\" width=600 height=90 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2759900/extras/48ed19f33d115b35dade0ab21179f89d.poster.avif?t=1749946732\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2759900/extras/48ed19f33d115b35dade0ab21179f89d.webm?t=1749946732\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2759900/extras/48ed19f33d115b35dade0ab21179f89d.mp4?t=1749946732\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>A clicker game about everybody's favorite <i>probably </i>fictional actor! Click to gain \"Leo's\" which can be used as currency for such things as:<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><i>Items at the shop!</i><br></li><li> <i>The settings menu</i>!<br></li><li> <i>Hey, what does this <strong>giant ominous door</strong> do..?</i></li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2759900/extras/80ff89f9440ae6eeb4e2bc90ad8fddc5.avif?t=1749946732\" width=600 height=90 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2759900/extras/9443fb2473a01aaed7be5a136a642a26.poster.avif?t=1749946732\" width=600 height=272 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2759900/extras/9443fb2473a01aaed7be5a136a642a26.webm?t=1749946732\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2759900/extras/9443fb2473a01aaed7be5a136a642a26.mp4?t=1749946732\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>A simple runner game with <strong>3 maps</strong>, <strong>4 skins</strong>, and <strong>a lingering question...</strong><br><br><i>...can you escape Joe Biden...?</i><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2759900/extras/b77502139082d559ce47a9b4f9ea270d.avif?t=1749946732\" width=600 height=135 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2759900/extras/662f3fcc5f810a08e2ca242f72b1ce73.poster.avif?t=1749946732\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2759900/extras/662f3fcc5f810a08e2ca242f72b1ce73.webm?t=1749946732\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2759900/extras/662f3fcc5f810a08e2ca242f72b1ce73.mp4?t=1749946732\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong><i>Now with voice acting by Blumpflerdinko!</i></strong><br><br>Get your <strong>notebooks out</strong> and your <strong>thinking caps on</strong>! In this <strong>radical</strong> math experience, you'll power through 30 problems- easy and hard- to become a <strong>math wizard</strong>! What mathtastical secrets await you in this fractional journey?<br><br>(yes the gameplay is literally just doing math)<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2759900/extras/acc257be9541c8b1e64a5bbad7c8d2bc.avif?t=1749946732\" width=600 height=135 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2759900/extras/58779666dbb488eadd5560dbdd1d9b30.poster.avif?t=1749946732\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2759900/extras/58779666dbb488eadd5560dbdd1d9b30.webm?t=1749946732\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2759900/extras/58779666dbb488eadd5560dbdd1d9b30.mp4?t=1749946732\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>In this maze game, you'll have to navigate the corridors of your office all the while <strong>avoiding security camera and bosses</strong> to reach the bathroom in time. Oh, and <strong>don't mind the crazies</strong>. They're not there for any reason in particular.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2759900/extras/4d0fddb9dc1b7065946de4ea9b5b0a9b.avif?t=1749946732\" width=600 height=135 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2759900/extras/74652e5397404708c07075a909555e94.webp?t=1749946732\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2759900/extras/74652e5397404708c07075a909555e94.poster.avif?t=1749946732\" class=\"bb_img\" width=600 height=256 /></picture></span><br><br><br>Play as a Pennsylvania driver as you <strong>attempt to run over pedestrians and cows</strong> all the while avoiding the all-too-common Pennsylvania inconveniences of <strong>potholes</strong>. Can you collect <strong>10 Pennsylvania Points</strong> and become the most \"Pennsylvanian\" Pennsylvania driver of all time?",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2759900/extras/3e2987d95a497ac8eb513390b721555f.apng?t=1749946732\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2759900/extras/3e2987d95a497ac8eb513390b721555f.poster.avif?t=1749946732\" class=\"bb_img\" width=600 height=90 /></picture></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2759900/extras/baa022df344ba968f360309a57916221.poster.avif?t=1749946732\" width=600 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2759900/extras/baa022df344ba968f360309a57916221.webm?t=1749946732\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2759900/extras/baa022df344ba968f360309a57916221.mp4?t=1749946732\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Five goofy little adventures spanning a variety of genres (5, in fact) await! Even if these games <i>really</i> sucked that's not a half-bad deal!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2759900/extras/4189c14c0fd2c2a67a454ddee4777424.avif?t=1749946732\" width=600 height=90 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2759900/extras/48ed19f33d115b35dade0ab21179f89d.poster.avif?t=1749946732\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2759900/extras/48ed19f33d115b35dade0ab21179f89d.webm?t=1749946732\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2759900/extras/48ed19f33d115b35dade0ab21179f89d.mp4?t=174994